Package: slitherlinkshiny
Title: Interactive Web Application for the Slitherlink Puzzle
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Marouane", "Daoudi", , "marouane.daoudi@etu.umontpellier.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implementation of the Slitherlink logic puzzle. This package provides a mathematical engine to model the grids and validate topological rules, as well as an interactive web interface developed with Shiny.
